<h4 id="orientation-helping-new-users-to-get-started">Orientation: Helping new users to get started</h4>

<p>â€¢ The old design: When the novice users first visited the app, the empty state screens did not offer much help with what should be done next. 
<br />â€¢ The new design has a landing screen which guides the new user to explore the app features with simple 3 videos and a set of simple steps they need to complete to start earning. This screen evolves as the user progresses through each step. This also helps novice users to get started with the app without needing a telephonic orientation.</p>

<figure class="half ">
  
    
      <a href="/assets/img/projects/onboarding/onboarding-landing1.png" title="Landing - Before">
