<h4 id="self-verification-transparent-simple-and-easy">Self-verification: Transparent, Simple and easy</h4>

<p>â€¢ Our top most priority was to get as many users as possible to self-verify and start earning from our platform. 
<br />â€¢ The old design did not offer nudges in the right places. The design also did not offer clarity on the verification process itself and the need for verification.
<br />â€¢ The new design offered a lot of clarity in the process of verification and gave users a simple todo list to complete. The UX copy also focused on ensuring the users were well informed on what they had to do and what will happen next.</p>

<figure class="half ">
  
    
