<div class="block_text-container">
<h2>Learnings &amp; Takeaways &nbsp; <div class="long_dash"></div></h2>
    <div class="block_text">
â€¢ Keeping users well informed builds trust and confidence in the platform. 
<br />â€¢ Clear CTAs make it easier for users to complete actions.
<br />â€¢ UX Copy plays a huge role in giving transparency and building trust. 
<br /><br />
With these changes we were able to see an increase in self verification to 20% (and still growing at the time of writing this report)
The next steps would be to explore the auto verification or bank account and capturing the KYC details from uploaded images. 
